articles.title: US and Iran at 'last exit before the tunnel', says admiral
articles.description: Adm. James Stavridis discusses Iran's firing of more than a dozen ballistic missiles at two Iraqi air bases housing U.S. forces and why he says is Iran is neither reckless nor suicidal.

articles.title: Iran fires missiles; Trump tweets 'All is well!', will make Weds. statement
articles.description: Iran retaliated for the killing of a top general by firing more than a dozen ballistic missiles at two Iraqi air bases housing U.S. forces on Wednesday local time. Mika Brzezinski discusses.
